### ─────────────────────────────
### AUTH
### ─────────────────────────────

### Registrar usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Registrar usuário 2 — Vasco
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Vasco da Gama",
