### Meus dados
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─────────────────────────────
### PROJETOS
### ─────────────────────────────

### Listar projetos (público, com paginação)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?page=1&limit=10

### Buscar com filtro
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?search=api

### Criar projeto
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Meu Projeto C2",
  "description": "API desenvolvida por Otávio"
}

### Buscar projeto por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/cmpn7ikjw000214h2jwkrf309

### Atualizar projeto
PUT {{baseUrl}}/projects/cmpn7ikjw000214h2jwkrf309
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Título Atualizado"
}

### Deletar projeto (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/cmpn7ikjw000214h2jwkrf309
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─────────────────────────────
### TAREFAS
### ─────────────────────────────

### Listar tarefas do projeto
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/cmpn7ikjw000214h2jwkrf309/tasks

### Criar tarefa
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/cmpn7ikjw000214h2jwkrf309/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Finalizar apresentação",
  "description": "Rezar para dar certo",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "status": "PENDING",
  "dueData": "2020-06-01T23:59:00Z"
}

### Atualizar status da tarefa
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/projects/cmpn7ikjw000214h2jwkrf309/tasks/cmpn7kdmn000414h2fxo3ohx3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "DONE"
}

### Deletar tarefa
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/projects/cmpn7ikjw000214h2jwkrf309/tasks/cmpn7kdmn000414h2fxo3ohx3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─────────────────────────────
### ADMIN
### ─────────────────────────────

### Listar todos os usuários (ADMIN only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
